      "content": "i get that, but i already had my blood work done a few months ago and they said i was low. if i just do the high dose for like 10-14 days max, would the body really react that badly? i feel like it's just a huge surplus that'll get used up, it's not like i'm taking it forever. i just need a quick boost because i'm already feeling really run down.",
